org.forgerock.openidm.jaspi.config

Class OSGiAuthnFilterBuilder

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.forgerock.openidm.jaspi.config.OSGiAuthnFilterBuilder
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    OSGiAuthnFilterHelper

    @Properties(value={@Property(name="service.vendor",value="ForgeRock AS."),@Property(name="service.description",value="OpenIDM Commons Authentication Filter Configuration")})
public class OSGiAuthnFilterBuilder
extends Object
implements OSGiAuthnFilterHelper
    Configures the authentication chains based on configuration obtained through OSGi. Example: 
         
 {
     "serverAuthConfig" : {
         "scriptExtensions" : {
             "augmentSecurityContext" : {
                 "type" : "text/javascript",
                 "file" : "auth/authnPopulateContext.js"
             }
         },
         "sessionModule" : {
             "name" : "JWT_SESSION",
                 "properties" : {
                     "someSetting" : "some-value"
                 }
         },
         "authModules" : [
             {
                 "name" : "IWA",
                 "properties" : {
                     "someSetting" : "some-value"
                 }
             },
             {
                 "name" : "PASSTHROUGH",
                 "properties" : {
                     "someSetting" : "some-value"
                 }
             }
         ]
     }
 }
    Also, 
         
         OSGiAuthnFilterBuilder.getInstance()
    may be used to inject the OSGi dependencies into other modules as an OSGiAuthnFilterHelper.
